  "text": "To develop the oracle rule, we consider two problems in turn: (i) what is oracle statistic that gives the optimal ranking of all tests? (ii) What is the oracle cutoff that controls the FDR and maximizes the ETP? Consider model (1). Suppose we obtain a z-value from each test. [CITATION_1] showed that the optimal test statistic in the oracle setting is the local false discovery rate",
